.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: grey, emerald, lilac, purple, turquise
There are 5 different nationalities: russian, polish, argentine, chinese, british
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, turquisemaster, aristoff, swisher, siglo
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, almond-milk, hot-chocolate, sprite
5 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, cat, snake, frog

1. the russian is the person who likes grey
2. the polish is the owner of the bird
3. the person drinking 7up is the person who likes emerald
4. the argentine is the person drinking cola
5. the person who likes emerald is to the right of the person who likes lilac
6. the bongani-smoker is the owner of the frog
7. the turquisemaster-smoker is the person who likes purple
8. the person drinking almond-milk is in the middle
9. the chinese is on the far left
10. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret
11. the turquisemaster-smoker is to the left or right of the owner of the snake
12. the swisher-smoker is the person drinking hot-chocolate
13. the british is the siglo-smoker
14. the chinese is to the left or right of the person who likes turquise

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Nationality	|   chinese	|    argentine	|     russian	|    polish	|    british	|
| Color		|    purple	|      turquise	|      grey	|     lilac	|     emerald	|
| Beverage	|     sprite	|      cola	|      almond-milk	| hot-chocolate	|     7up	|
| Cigar		|     turquisemaster	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| swisher	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     ferret	|     snake	|     frog	|     bird	|     cat	|
